ecial (song)|Midnight Special Train]]\"<br /><small>b/w \"Feeling Happy\"</small>\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| align=\"left\"|''Rock & Roll''\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\"| 1957\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| \"After a While\"<br /><small>b/w \"Red Sails in the Sunset\"</small>\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| align=\"left\" rowspan=\"5\"|''Rockin' the Blues''\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| \"Love Roller Coaster\"<br /><small>b/w \"World of Trouble\"</small>\n| \u2014\n| 12\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| \"Trouble in Mind\"<br /><small>b/w \"I Need a Girl\"</small>\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| \"Teen Age Letter\"<br /><small>b/w \"Wee Baby Blues\" (from ''The Boss of the Blues Sings Kansas City Jazz'')</small>\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n|-\n|| 1958\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| \"Jump for Joy\"<br /><small>b/w \"Blues in the Night\"</small>\n| \u2014\n| 15\n|-\n|| 1959\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| \"Got You on My Mind\"<br /><small>b/w \"Love Oh Careless Love\"</small>\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| align=\"left\" rowspan=\"4\"|''Rhythm & Blues Years''\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 1960\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| \"Honey Hush\" <small>(Re-recording)</small><br /><small>b/w \"Tomorrow Night\"</small>\n| 53\n| \u2014\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| \"Chains of Love\"<br /><small>b/w \"My Little Honey Dripper\"</small>\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| \"My Reason for Living\"<br /><small>b/w \"Sweet Sue\"</small>\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|1964\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| \"I'm Packin' Up\"<br /><small>b/w \"I Walk a Lonely Mile\"</small>\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| align=\"left\" rowspan=\"2\"|Non-album tracks\n|-\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| \"Shake Rattle and Roll\"<small> (rerecording)</small><br /><small>b/w \"There'll Be Some Tears Falling\"</small>\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n|-\n|| 1967\n| style=\"text-align:left;\"| \"Big Wheel\"<br /><small>b/w \"Bluer Than Blue\"</small>\n| \u2014\n| \u2014\n| align=\"left\"|''Singing the Blues''\n|