aratahs/squad | title=Player Profiles | work=NSW Waratahs | accessdate=14 February 2018 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180214054958/http://www.nswwaratahs.com.au/waratahs/squad | archivedate=14 February 2018 | url-status=live | df=dmy-all }}</ref><ref name=\"Australian squads finalised for 2018 Vodafone Super Rugby season\">{{cite press release | url=http://www.rugbyaustralia.com.au/MediaReleases/Article/tabid/1699/ArticleID/18394/AUSTRALIAN-SQUADS-FINALISED-FOR-2018-VODAFONE-SUPER-RUGBY-SEASON.aspx | title=Australian squads finalised for 2018 Vodafone Super Rugby season | publisher=Rugby Australia | date=21 February 2018 | accessdate=22 February 2018 | archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180222031301/http://www.rugbyaustralia.com.au/MediaReleases/Article/tabid/1699/ArticleID/18394/AUSTRALIAN-SQUADS-FINALISED-FOR-2018-VODAFONE-SUPER-RUGBY-SEASON.aspx | archivedate=22 February 2018 | url-status=live | df=dmy-all}}</ref>{{efn|group=Squad|name=Duffy|Duffy was not included in the original squad, but was named in their matchday squad for their match against the {{Rut Jaguares}}.<ref name=\"NSW Waratahs team named to face Jaguares\">{{cite press release | url=http://www.nswwaratahs.com.au/news/news-article/articleid/17959/nsw-waratahs-team-named-to-face-jaguares | title=NSW Waratahs team named to face Jaguares | publisher=NSW Waratahs | date=9 March 2018 | accessdate=28 March 2018}}</ref>}}{{efn|group=Squad|name=Snowden|Snowden was not included in the original squad, but was named in their matchday squad for their match against the {{Rut Rebels}}.<ref name=\"NSW Waratahs name team to face Melbourne Rebels\">{{cite press release | url=http://www.nswwaratahs.com.au/news/news-article/articleid/17969/nsw-waratahs-name-team-to-face-melbourne-rebels | title=NSW Waratahs name team to face Melbourne Rebels | publisher=NSW Waratahs | date=16 March 2018 | accessdate=28 March 2018}}</ref>}}{{efn|group=Squad|name=Tawake|Tawake was not included in the original squad, 