ers|Nevers]]\n|align=left|\n|-\n|align=left|{{flagdeco|AUS}} {{sortname|Matt|Lucas|Matt Lucas (rugby union)}}\n|align=left|[[Scrum-half (rugby union)|Scrum-half]]\n|align=left|[[Brumbies]]\n|align=left| \n|-\n|align=left|{{flagdeco|AUS}} {{sortname|Andrew|Deegan}}\n|align=left|[[Fly-half (rugby union)|Fly-half]]\n|align=left|{{flagdeco|IRE|rugby union}} [[Connacht Rugby|Connacht]]\n|align=left| \n|-\n|align=left|{{flagdeco|AUS}} {{sortname|Rob|Horne}}\n|align=left|[[Centre (rugby union)|Centre]]\n|align=left|{{flagdeco|ENG}} [[Northampton Saints]]\n|align=left|\n|-\n|align=left|{{flagdeco|AUS}} {{sortname|Dave|Horwitz|David Horwitz}}\n|align=left|[[Centre (rugby union)|Centre]]\n|align=left|[[Melbourne Rebels|Rebels]]\n|align=left|\n|-\n|align=left|{{flagdeco|AUS}} {{sortname|Reece|Robinson}}\n|align=left|[[Wing (rugby union)|Wing]]\n|align=left|[[Sydney Roosters]] ([[National Rugby League|NRL]])\n|align=left|\n|-\n|align=left|{{flagdeco|AUS}} {{sortname|Harry|Jones|Harry Jones (rugby union, born 1995)}}\n|align=left|[[Fullback (rugby union)|Fullback]]\n|align=left|{{flagdeco|JPN}} [[Toyota Industries Shuttles|Toyota Jido Shokki]]\n|align=left|\n|}\n{{col-end}}\n\n==Season summary==\n{{Main article|List of 2018 Super Rugby matches}}\n===Season results===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"font-size:95%;\"\n|-\n!scope=col|{{abbr|Rnd|Round}}\n!scope=col|Date & local time\n!scope=col| \n!scope=col|Team\n!scope=col|Score\n!scope=col|Venue\n!scope=col|Attendance\n!scope=col|{{abbr|Ref.|Reference}}\n|-\n|align=center|[[List of 2018 Super Rugby matches#Round 1|1]]\n|align=center colspan=\"7\"|''Bye''\n|- style=\"background:#cfc;\"\n|align=center|[[List of 2018 Super Rugby matches#Round 2|2]]\n|align=left|Saturday, 24 February (7:45 pm) \n|align=center|H\n|align=left|{{flagdeco|RSA}} [[Stormers]]\n|align=center|'''34'''\u201327\n|align=left|[[Sydney Football Stadium|Allianz Stadium]], [[Sydney]], [[New South Wales]], Australia\n|align=center|11,087\n|align=cent